parameters.name: EndDate
parameters.description: Required, end time, format is yyyy-MM-dd, default is yyyy-MM-dd 00:00:00, the query interval cannot exceed 90 days.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: Number of items per page, default is 10.

parameters.name: StartDate
parameters.description: Required, start time, format is yyyy-MM-dd, default is yyyy-MM-dd 00:00:00, the query interval cannot exceed 90 days.
